install pip:
apt-get update
apt-get -y install python-pip

install youtube-dl
https://github.com/rg3/youtube-dl/blob/master/README.md#how-do-i-update-youtube-dl
sudo pip install -U youtube-dl

to uninstall youtube-dl
sudo apt-get remove -y youtube-dl


cd my/path/to/music/folder
Make sure to install youtube-dl and ffmpeg beforehand.
If you get 'index' is not recognized as an internal or batch command, then enclose the URL inside "".
youtube-dl -i --yes-playlist -x -f bestaudio --audio-format "mp3" ""
example:
youtube-dl -i --yes-playlist -x -f bestaudio --audio-format "mp3" "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=psuRGfAaju4&index=1&list=PL70A21963BE29EE48"
